item.title: Be a part of MSHacks 2.0
item.description: MS Hacks 2.0 is one of the biggest event that is conducted by Microsoft Student Technical Community of LPU. The sole aim of this hackathon is to provide a competitive environment where students from all the domains come together and build something innovative. We encourage the students to build problems that can solve real-life challenges for users. We aim to build better future with Technology. Are you in? Register Now ...
